    "ios_step1": "从 App Store 下载 <a href='https://apps.apple.com/us/app/stream-network-debug-tool/id1312141691' target='_blank' class='underline text-blue-600'>Stream</a> 应用。",
    "ios_step2": "打开应用并允许在系统设置中配置 VPN（“设置” -> “通用” -> “VPN与设备管理”）。",
    "ios_step3": "配置 HTTPS 抓包（安装证书）：",
    "ios_step3_1": "在 Stream 应用中点击 Sniff Now。",
    "ios_step3_2": "允许添加配置。",
    "ios_step3_3": "点击“Install CA” -> “Install CA Certificate” -> “允许”。",
    "ios_step4": "前往“设置” -> “通用” -> “VPN与设备管理” -> 点击 Stream Generated CA 并安装描述文件。",
    "ios_step5": "前往“设置” -> “通用” -> “关于本机” -> “证书信任设置” -> 打开 Stream Generated CA 旁边的开关。",
    "ios_step6": "启动《明日方舟：终末地》，打开寻访记录页面并保持开启。",
    "ios_step7": "返回 Stream 应用并点击巨大的 Sniff Now 按钮。",
    "ios_step8": "返回游戏并刷新历史页面（切换标签页或重新打开）。",
    "ios_step9": "返回 Stream 并点击 Stop Sniffing。",
    "ios_step10": "前往 Sniff History。找到以 <span class='bg-gray-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 dark:bg-[#343434] dark:border-[#444444] dark:text-[#E0E0E0] rounded text-sm font-mono text-gray-600 border border-gray-200 select-all break-all whitespace-normal inline-block'>https://ef-webview.gryphline.com</span> 开头的请求。",
    "ios_step11": "打开它，前往 Request 标签页，并复制链接（以 https 开头）。",
    "ios_step12": "将获取到的链接粘贴在下方",
